# Privacy-sensitive runtime data: only README/example files are tracked.
# This directory contains real ingested evidence at runtime and must never
# be committed, even when the source data is synthetic. See
# docs/adr/ADR-0002-data-as-code-separation.md and PROJECT_CHARTER.md
# Section 9 (data sensitivity as an adoption blocker).
data/raw/*
!data/raw/README.md
data/processed/*
!data/processed/README.md
assessments/*
!assessments/README.md
reports/*
!reports/README.md

# Sample evidence is intentionally tracked (synthetic/public only) but any
# accidental non-synthetic upload should still never land here by design.
